#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.gammainc.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.gammainc"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammainc:1 of
msgid "Regularized lower incomplete gamma function."
msgstr "正则化下不完全伽马函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammainc:3 of
msgid "It is defined as"
msgstr "其定义为"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammainc:5 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid "P(a, x) = \\frac{1}{\\Gamma(a)} \\int_0^x t^{a - 1}e^{-t} dt"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammainc:9 of
msgid "for :math:`a > 0` and :math:`x \\geq 0`. See [dlmf]_ for details."
msgstr "对于 :math:`a > 0` 且 :math:`x \\geq 0`。详见 [dlmf]_。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.gammainc.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammainc:11 of
msgid "Positive parameter"
msgstr "正参数"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammainc:13 of
msgid "Nonnegative argument"
msgstr "非负参数"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammainc:15 of
msgid "Optional output array for the function values"
msgstr "函数值的可选输出数组"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.gammainc.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammainc:18 of
msgid "Values of the lower incomplete gamma function"
msgstr "下不完全伽马函数的值"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.gammainc.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammainc:23 of
msgid ":func:`gammaincc`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammainc:24 of
msgid "regularized upper incomplete gamma function"
msgstr "正则化上不完全伽马函数"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammainc:26 of
msgid ":func:`gammaincinv`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammainc:27 of
msgid "inverse of the regularized lower incomplete gamma function"
msgstr "正则化下不完全伽马函数的逆函数"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammainc:29 of
msgid ":func:`gammainccinv`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammainc:30 of
msgid "inverse of the regularized upper incomplete gamma function"
msgstr "正则化上不完全伽马函数的逆函数"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammainc:33 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammainc:34 of
msgid ""
"The function satisfies the relation ``gammainc(a, x) + gammaincc(a, x) = "
"1`` where `gammaincc` is the regularized upper incomplete gamma function."
msgstr ""
"该函数满足关系式 ``gammainc(a, x) + gammaincc(a, x) = 1``，其中 `"
"gammaincc` 是正则化上不完全伽马函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammainc:38 of
msgid "The implementation largely follows that of [boost]_."
msgstr "该实现主要遵循 [boost]_ 的方法。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammainc:40 of
msgid ""
"`gammainc` has experimental support for Python Array API Standard "
"compatible backends in addition to NumPy. Please consider testing these "
"features by setting an environment variable ``SCIPY_ARRAY_API=1`` and "
"providing CuPy, PyTorch, JAX, or Dask arrays as array arguments. The "
"following combinations of backend and device (or other capability) are "
"supported."
msgstr ""
"`gammainc` 除了支持 NumPy 外，还对 Python Array API Standard 兼容的后端"
"提供实验性支持。请考虑通过设置环境变量 ``SCIPY_ARRAY_API=1`` 并提供 CuPy"
"、PyTorch、JAX 或 Dask 数组作为参数来测试这些功能。当前支持以下后端与设备"
"（或其他能力）的组合。"

